msgid "在能得到相同效果（如平移而非旋转）时， :class:`~.DataUpdater` 的性能会优于 :class:`~.GroupUpdater`。"
msgstr ""
"When the same effect can be achieved (such as translation rather than "
"rotation), :class:`~.DataUpdater` will perform better than "
":class:`~.GroupUpdater`."

